WEBVTT

01:38.011 --> 01:40.521
<b>Febreezy</b>

01:40.521 --> 01:42.311
<b><i>Deodorizer?</i></b>

01:42.311 --> 01:44.771
<b>Um, Yamada-san?</b>

01:45.631 --> 01:47.021
<b>Do I...</b>

01:47.021 --> 01:51.301
<b>Um, how do I put this?</b>

01:52.801 --> 01:55.581
<b>Actually, never mind.</b>

01:58.001 --> 02:01.821
<b>With the bag, your total 
comes to 1,563 yen.</b>

02:02.541 --> 02:03.481
<b>Right.</b>

02:04.091 --> 02:07.621
<b><i>It's not something I can ask 
someone who's on the clock.</i></b>

02:10.751 --> 02:13.051
<b>Here's your change and receipt.</b>

02:14.171 --> 02:15.551
<b>Thank you for shopping with us.</b>

02:16.361 --> 02:17.491
<b>Thank you.</b>

02:23.061 --> 02:25.981
<b>Shit Workplace</b>

02:23.791 --> 02:25.651
<b><i>Shit workplace,</i></b>

02:25.601 --> 02:28.481
<b>Power-Drunk Boss</b>

02:26.161 --> 02:27.961
<b><i>shit boss.</i></b>

02:28.061 --> 02:30.981
<b>Deodorizer</b>

02:28.711 --> 02:31.171
<b><i>Now, deodorizer.</i></b>

02:30.611 --> 02:33.071
<b>Question</b>

02:31.171 --> 02:33.071
<b><i>And a question on the tip of his tongue.</i></b>

02:38.501 --> 02:40.081
<b><i>I think I've got it.</i></b>

02:41.611 --> 02:43.081
<b>Sasaki-san.</b>

02:43.331 --> 02:45.331
<b>Did somebody say you reeked of cigarettes?</b>

02:48.211 --> 02:51.401
<b>Are you a mind reader, Tayama-san?</b>

02:53.071 --> 02:56.221
<b>Compared to you, everybody else 
is somewhat of a mind reader.</b>

02:57.571 --> 03:00.941
<b>I just saw you picking up 
deodorizer in there.</b>

03:01.801 --> 03:03.301
<b>From where?</b>

03:03.301 --> 03:05.601
<b><i>Hey, it's not a lie.</i></b>

03:08.101 --> 03:11.631
<b>Anyway, you're right. 
My boss hates the concept of smoking.</b>

03:11.631 --> 03:14.741
<b>He yelled at me, saying, 
"You reek! Do something about it!"</b>

03:14.741 --> 03:16.221
<b><i>Wow, I hit the bull's-eye.</i></b>

03:17.431 --> 03:20.341
<b>Well, it's the fate of all 
smokers everywhere.</b>

03:26.821 --> 03:30.691
<b>If you brush your teeth after you smoke, 
you'll get rid of most of the stench.</b>

03:32.041 --> 03:35.421
<b>Then just spray your clothes, 
and you're good to go.</b>

03:35.421 --> 03:37.301
<b>But sometimes...</b>

03:39.031 --> 03:42.251
<b>you get the whiners 
like I did the other... day?</b>

03:43.511 --> 03:45.761
<b>You're incredible, Tayama-san!</b>

03:45.761 --> 03:48.271
<b>It's so cool that you know all this!</b>

03:48.621 --> 03:52.281
<b>Eh, I'm just passing on a senpai's advice.</b>

03:55.441 --> 03:58.741
<b>But you're the one who told me.</b>

04:05.851 --> 04:07.911
<b>Sasaki-san, shake.</b>

04:07.911 --> 04:10.181
<b>Huh? O-Okay?</b>

04:10.671 --> 04:14.001
<b>Wait, "shake"? Tayama-san?</b>

04:15.591 --> 04:16.921
<b>For you.</b>

04:17.341 --> 04:19.771
<b>It's the deodorizing mist I use.</b>

04:21.611 --> 04:23.761
<b>It looks expensive. Are you sure?</b>

04:23.761 --> 04:26.761
<b>No biggie. It's half-empty, 
and I have more at home.</b>

04:27.381 --> 04:31.941
<b>Thank you. This is so fancy.</b>

04:32.361 --> 04:37.181
<b>As long as you don't go overboard, 
nobody at work will notice the scent.</b>

04:38.951 --> 04:40.491
<b>Do you like how it smells?</b>

04:41.461 --> 04:43.651
<b>What scent is it?</b>

04:43.651 --> 04:45.091
<b>Wanna check?</b>

04:47.021 --> 04:50.081
<b>I usually spray it 
around here, so feel free.</b>

04:52.381 --> 04:54.341
<b>I'm not going to sniff you!</b>

04:54.341 --> 04:58.591
<b>Aw, I thought you'd go for it.</b>

04:59.731 --> 05:04.091
<b>Tayama-san, do you see me 
as a dog or something?</b>

05:10.061 --> 05:12.101
<b>A Labrador retriever, maybe?</b>

05:12.101 --> 05:15.361
<b>Huh? Wh-What's that?</b>

05:15.361 --> 05:16.201
<b>A dog breed.</b>

05:16.201 --> 05:18.311
<b>So I was right!</b>

05:20.861 --> 05:23.111
<b>Genki Trading</b>

05:41.991 --> 05:44.631
<b><i>Now I just spray this.</i></b>

05:45.761 --> 05:51.021
<b><i>Wait... She said not to go overboard, 
but how much is the normal amount?</i></b>

05:51.391 --> 05:54.531
<b><i>It's easy to tell with my 
usual deodorizing sprays.</i></b>

05:55.941 --> 05:57.411
<b>Wow, somebody's fashionable.</b>

05:57.411 --> 05:58.651
<b>Whoa! Suzuki?</b>

06:00.561 --> 06:05.741
<b>Telling us smokers we reek is basically 
the chief's way of saying good morning!</b>

06:05.741 --> 06:07.951
<b>Don't take it so seriously, man!</b>

06:07.951 --> 06:10.661
<b>But just think about it.</b>

06:10.661 --> 06:15.181
<b>Brush your teeth after you smoke 
and apply some of this mist,</b>

06:15.181 --> 06:19.461
<b>and voilà, you've got your scent care 
down pat, or so I've heard.</b>

06:19.461 --> 06:21.711
<b>Heard? From whom?</b>

06:19.461 --> 06:21.711
<b>No smoking
in the restroom</b>

06:21.711 --> 06:24.311
<b>Huh? Uh, well...</b>

06:25.471 --> 06:27.971
<b>m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100</b>

06:25.471 --> 06:27.971
<b>Tayama-san [Tayama] (Name)

Supermarket worker I smoke with
(section unknown). She teases me
but is in general very nice.</b>

06:25.631 --> 06:27.971
<b><i>Just you try introducing me.</i></b>

06:29.711 --> 06:30.461
<b>Take that.</b>

06:30.851 --> 06:34.731
<b>That's cold! What the hell was that for?!</b>

06:34.731 --> 06:38.001
<b>Wow, that smells great!</b>

06:38.001 --> 06:39.861
<b>If you go home smelling so good,</b>

06:39.861 --> 06:42.781
<b>your wife'll fall in love 
with you all over again!</b>

06:44.091 --> 06:48.741
<b>Don't be stupid. Keiko-chan's 
already head over heels for me.</b>

06:49.541 --> 06:53.811
<b>But I don't particularly mind 
if she moves up to the next stage of love!</b>

06:56.531 --> 06:58.631
<b>Tell me more, buddy.</b>

06:58.631 --> 07:02.591
<b>Like I said, brush your teeth 
and use a mist.</b>

07:02.591 --> 07:04.011
<b>Just like this.</b>

07:07.761 --> 07:10.391
<b>24-Hour</b>

07:07.761 --> 07:10.391
<b>Supermarket S</b>

07:08.741 --> 07:10.391
<b>Welcome!</b>

07:10.921 --> 07:13.021
<b>Here's your change and receipt.</b>

07:13.311 --> 07:14.951
<b>Thank you.</b>

07:15.551 --> 07:16.601
<b>Huh?</b>

07:17.021 --> 07:22.651
<b>Sasaki-san, you kind of smell 
like Tayama-chan today.</b>

07:24.151 --> 07:29.911
<b><i>No! That's just because... 
Gah! I'm so embarrassed!</i></b>

07:31.671 --> 07:33.871
<b>Oh, I got this mist from her 
the other day,</b>

07:33.871 --> 07:36.761
<b>but I didn't get to ask her 
how much of it to use.</b>

07:37.921 --> 07:40.261
<b>I guess I used too much today.</b>

07:45.621 --> 07:49.331
<b>S-Sorry about that! Thank you!</b>

07:52.721 --> 07:55.561
<b>Yamada-chan, you can clock out.</b>

07:57.051 --> 07:59.771
<b>Are you okay? Did something happen?</b>

07:59.771 --> 08:00.561
<b>No...</b>

08:01.331 --> 08:04.821
<b>I just wanted to tease a little, but...</b>

08:05.491 --> 08:09.151
<b>That reaction actually made me blush, too.</b>

09:21.151 --> 09:24.091
<b><i>I owe Master Tayama big time.</i></b>

09:24.941 --> 09:26.771
<b>Etiquette Master</b>

09:27.711 --> 09:31.411
<b><i>I hope she'll like my return gift.</i></b>

09:36.531 --> 09:38.541
<b>Tayama-san, good even...</b>

09:38.541 --> 09:39.421
<b>Huh?</b>

09:40.891 --> 09:42.791
<b><i>What?!</i></b>

09:42.791 --> 09:47.041
<b><i>A-A-A different employee?!</i></b>

09:47.661 --> 09:51.291
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

09:51.791 --> 09:55.421
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

09:56.131 --> 09:59.381
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
